Tga '''Tizi Uzzu''' nɣ '''Tizi n Uzezzu''' yat tmdint ɣ tmazirt n lqbayl ɣ [[Dzayr]]. Tg tamdint akkʷ imqqurn ɣ tmazirt n lqbayl, d tmaẓunt n ''twilayt n Tizi n uzzu''. taggug f [[dzayr tamaẓunt]] s 100 km, d 125 km f [[Bgayt]].
== Ism ==
Tizi Uzzu iga yism amaziɣ, ikka d yism ad ''Tizi + n + Uzezzu,'' suln kra n iḍwwaṛn ɣ tmazrit n lqbayl ar as aqqran ''Tizi n Uzezzu'' macc amata n imzdaɣn n tmazirt-ad ar as aqqran "''Tizi Wezzu''" Azezzu iga yan wanaw n [[ijjign]].

==Tamallayt==
Idrarn n Djardjar d akkʷ tasgiwin nnsn gan-t aɣbalu n tmallayt imqqurn ɣ tmdint n Tizi Uzzu imi kraygat usggas kigan n middn ar sr-s ttmuddun bac ad zzrin akud n tigga-nnsn. Taddart n Tala n yilf akk-d Tikejda d imukan lli iɛejben kigan n midden ɣ tizi n Skii. 

Imukan n taɣedweft: Lwert Arumani: Tigzirt (Iomnium), Taqsebt (Rusupisir), Azzefun (Rosazu). Rrif n lebḥer (taftist) d ayen i ijebbden daɣen aṭas n middn di tamurt merra.

==Amzruy==
Iɣrm n Tizi Wezzu ityawssan bedda s imaziɣen Li usinin asafu n tmagit n imazivn, imi ɣ tutlayt n iqbayliyn , Ulac ayen illan ɣ umzruy azayku n Tizi Wezzu, ar tinin waratn masd kra n lbni  itubna ɣ tizi n Irumaniyn. ɣ umzruy ad naf yan wemkan i yesɛan kra n tiggmma ɣ tizi n Iturkiyn; amkan agi yefka-d talalit i wmarci n dimanch akk-d yiwet Iɣrm (teɣremt) tamectuht, tella ar tura yiwet tiɣremt deg At Yiraten (azal n 25 km seg Tizi) i ttawbnan ɣ usggas 1850 ɣ tizi n taslkt Tafransist; tamdint agi tuɣal-ed teɣremt n Tizi Wezzu n tura.

